      <body>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><seg><seg rend="left"><pb facs="0021_FL81799616"/><hi rend="pre-print">Dr. Arthur Schnitzler</hi></seg><seg rend="right"><date>22. 12. 09</date></seg></seg><seg><hi rend="pre-print"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb133">Wien XVIII.
                        Spoettelgasse 7</rs>.</hi></seg></opener><p><salute>lieber Herr Doctor,</salute> wollen Sie an <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L03806-1"/><date>Din<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tag</date> (<date>28.</date>)<note type="commentary" corresp="K_L03806-1"><ref type="schnitzler-tagebuch" subtype="Cf" target="1909-12-28"/>.</note> zu mir ko<c rendition="#gemination-m">mm</c>en,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>o gegen
                  <time>½ 8</time> und gleich bei uns nachtmahlen?</p><p>Würde uns herzlich freuen.</p><closer>Ihr<lb/><signed>A. S.</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
